.us 1.4 Extraordinary right to withdraw deposits with a &fk01
.br
You may disregard an agreed notice period and can, without having to
pay an interest penalty, withdraw the amount from a deposit account with
a notice period if the interest rate is reduced before you can have the
the amount paid out.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
However, the amount must be withdrawn within 14 days after the entering
into force of the interest rate reduction.
